Here are the updates to address your requests.

### 1. Fix Emails (Backend)
I have updated the `EmailService` to include a **connection verification** check when the server starts. This will log exactly why emails aren't sending (e.g., "Invalid Login" or "Connection Timeout") to your server console. I also added a fallback to ensure it tries to send even if Redis isn't running.

### 2. Fix Vehicle "Generic" Name (Backend)
I updated the `ProductService`. It now uses a smarter logic to split vehicle names (`split(/\s+/)` instead of `split(' ')`), which handles accidental double spaces. It also handles single-word entries better.

### 3. Quick View Enhancements (Frontend)
I have completely upgraded the `QuickView` component:
